titles.title: Directing the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make a technical correction in the enrollment of H.R. 3060.

action.text: Mr. Walker asked unanimous consent to consider as introduced.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

vote.text: Resolution agreed to in Senate without amendment by Unanimous Consent.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.

bill.summary: 9/10/1996--Introduced. Makes a technical correction in the enrollment of H.R. 3060 (implementation of the Protocol on Environmental Protection to the Antarctic Treaty).
